00:30:46,740 --> 00:30:47,460
No.

564
00:30:47,780 --> 00:30:49,390
I... I'm afraid you'll hit me.

565
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:54,260
No, I wanted to apologize to you.

566
00:30:56,110 --> 00:30:57,260
I was too impulsive.

567
00:30:57,700 --> 00:31:00,460
I hit you
without understanding the situation.

568
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:01,350
Sorry.

569
00:31:02,630 --> 00:31:03,700
It doesn't matter.

570
00:31:03,700 --> 00:31:04,910
You did it for Qin.

571
00:31:04,910 --> 00:31:05,740
I can understand.

572
00:31:05,870 --> 00:31:06,910
You can understand, right?

573
00:31:07,780 --> 00:31:09,020
So I really can't bear

574
00:31:09,020 --> 00:31:10,390
to see Qin suffer any injustice.

575
00:31:10,780 --> 00:31:12,310
I apologize to you this time,

576
00:31:12,780 --> 00:31:13,590
but

577
00:31:13,590 --> 00:31:15,940
if such a thing happens in the future,

578
00:31:16,500 --> 00:31:18,260
you've seen what I'm capable of doing.

579
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:19,670
What are you guys talking about?

580
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:21,220
Hurry, sit.

581
00:31:21,740 --> 00:31:23,020
We're talking about

582
00:31:24,150 --> 00:31:25,940
sending you both some blessings

583
00:31:25,940 --> 00:31:28,740
and remind He Siyue.

584
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:32,540
What did they remind you?

585
00:31:32,830 --> 00:31:33,430
Nothing.

586
00:31:34,500 --> 00:31:35,540
Sorry.

587
00:31:36,740 --> 00:31:37,700
I'm late.

588
00:31:44,020 --> 00:31:44,700
Welcome.

589
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:47,910
Thank you for cooperating
with our campaign.

590
00:31:48,430 --> 00:31:49,180
It's my job.

591
00:31:49,390 --> 00:31:49,980
After all,

592
00:31:49,980 --> 00:31:52,310
I signed a contract
with your production team.

593
00:31:52,460 --> 00:31:54,500
I know a bit about the law.

594
00:31:55,700 --> 00:31:56,500
Besides,

595
00:31:57,220 --> 00:31:58,540
no one knows what the result will be

596
00:31:58,740 --> 00:32:00,500
until the end of the show.

597
00:32:02,020 --> 00:32:03,430
Now that everyone's here,

598
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:04,980
let's look at the trailer.

599
00:32:05,150 --> 00:32:06,910
We'll film
some footage of everyone together.

600
00:32:06,910 --> 00:32:07,590
Okay?

601
00:32:09,460 --> 00:32:10,150
Let's start.

602
00:32:13,050 --> 00:32:15,170
(Go Back Lover)

603
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:22,830
I'm Lu Xingyan.

604
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:25,070
I'm Shen Xingruo.

605
00:32:25,070 --> 00:32:26,180
I'm Xu Chengzhou.

606
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:27,220
I'm Chen Zhu.

607
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:28,020
I'm He Siyue.

608
00:32:28,020 --> 00:32:28,910
I'm Shi Qin.

609
00:32:30,390 --> 00:32:31,700
(Youth isn't a period of time)

610
00:32:31,910 --> 00:32:33,150
(for them,)

611
00:32:33,220 --> 00:32:34,350
(but a person.)

612
00:32:34,500 --> 00:32:35,910
(It's someone they'll fly)

613
00:32:35,910 --> 00:32:37,830
(thousands of miles to see)

614
00:32:37,910 --> 00:32:40,150
(and someone they can only see)

615
00:32:40,150 --> 00:32:41,460
(by taking a time machine.)

616
00:32:46,830 --> 00:32:48,980
This is the first time
we meet in Germany.

617
00:32:57,500 --> 00:32:59,740
The production team is really attentive.

618
00:32:59,910 --> 00:33:02,430
They even found
footage from "Race Against Time".

619
00:33:02,540 --> 00:33:03,910
I provided this material.

620
00:33:04,150 --> 00:33:05,150
I'll definitely be there

621
00:33:05,150 --> 00:33:07,110
for every important moment
of Xing's life.

622
00:33:07,150 --> 00:33:08,110
Good shot.

623
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:09,540
Lu Xingyan.

624
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:11,310
Tell me the truth.

625
00:33:11,460 --> 00:33:13,910
Did you already plan

626
00:33:14,020 --> 00:33:15,350
to win Xingruo back

627
00:33:15,350 --> 00:33:16,830
when you went on the show?

628
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:20,350
No, really.

629
00:33:20,700 --> 00:33:21,540
Really.

630
00:33:21,980 --> 00:33:24,910
I just wanted to cooperate at that time.

631
00:33:24,980 --> 00:33:26,350
Listen to his lies.

632
00:33:26,350 --> 00:33:27,940
Won't I know about his business?

633
00:33:27,940 --> 00:33:29,630
The first time
the production team called him,

634
00:33:29,630 --> 00:33:30,870
he was so nervous.

635
00:33:30,910 --> 00:33:31,870
It's like he was going on a blind date.

636
00:33:31,870 --> 00:33:33,590
He spent a long time
choosing just two outfits.

637
00:33:33,590 --> 00:33:34,740
He ended buying an entire outfit.

638
00:33:34,780 --> 00:33:35,730
Don't you think it's ridiculous?

639
00:33:36,220 --> 00:33:37,110
Enough.

640
00:33:37,500 --> 00:33:38,740
Tell me. I want to hear about it.

641
00:33:39,390 --> 00:33:39,980
Tell me.

642
00:33:40,110 --> 00:33:42,260
Okay, I'll tell you one more thing
since you want to hear.

643
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:44,020
Didn't Mr. Yu come?

644
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:45,150
We had a meal with Mr. Yu.

645
00:33:45,700 --> 00:33:46,910
Mr. Yu said

646
00:33:47,150 --> 00:33:48,630
he wants to move the show to Germany.

647
00:33:48,940 --> 00:33:49,670
Gosh.

648
00:33:49,670 --> 00:33:51,540
Lu Xingyan's face turned pale with fear.

649
00:33:51,910 --> 00:33:53,540
You don't know
how barren the entire resort was

650
00:33:53,540 --> 00:33:55,150
those two days.

651
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,150
You're quite good
at pretending to be calm.

652
00:33:57,150 --> 00:33:58,640
I didn't expect you
to be like this in private.

653
00:33:58,670 --> 00:34:00,740
I knew you were emotionally unstable.

654
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:03,310
My emotions
toward grass aren't that stable.

655
00:34:03,540 --> 00:34:05,220
So many things happened at that time,

656
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:06,430
why didn't you tell me?

657
00:34:07,430 --> 00:34:08,630
Why should I tell you?

658
00:34:08,910 --> 00:34:10,670
You have more pressure
producing the show than I do.

659
00:34:11,110 --> 00:34:12,740
There are many things
he didn't tell you.

660
00:34:12,740 --> 00:34:13,350
Tell me.

661
00:34:13,350 --> 00:34:15,190
Since you want to know, I'll tell you.

662
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:15,910
Go on.

663
00:34:16,910 --> 00:34:18,540
Didn't you break up with him
at that time?

664
00:34:18,540 --> 00:34:19,750
He kept asking me to drink with him.

665
00:34:19,750 --> 00:34:21,750
I asked him
to drink less and stop drinking.

666
00:34:21,750 --> 00:34:23,060
He said: "No.

667
00:34:23,100 --> 00:34:23,980
Only when I am intoxicated

668
00:34:23,980 --> 00:34:25,460
can I forget Shen Xingruo."

669
00:34:27,270 --> 00:34:28,020
You guys can chat.

670
00:34:28,620 --> 00:34:30,580
I know a cake shop that's delicious.

671
00:34:33,830 --> 00:34:34,830
Ask the driver to pick me up.

672
00:34:34,830 --> 00:34:35,910
My car is being serviced.

673
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:38,790
Isn't your car at the entrance?

674
00:34:38,790 --> 00:34:39,760
Yes, my car is at the entrance.

675
00:34:41,190 --> 00:34:41,710
Here.

676
00:34:42,230 --> 00:34:42,790
Thanks.

677
00:34:43,150 --> 00:34:44,890
Why did you
turn your right face 45 degrees

678
00:34:44,890 --> 00:34:46,010
to the camera just now?

679
00:34:46,860 --> 00:34:48,620
I did it for the audience to...

680
00:34:49,350 --> 00:34:50,910
Be safe.

681
00:34:51,230 --> 00:34:51,910
Bye.

682
00:34:51,910 --> 00:34:52,870
Hurry back.

683
00:34:52,870 --> 00:34:53,390
Besides...

684
00:34:56,940 --> 00:34:58,140
By the way...

685
00:34:58,620 --> 00:34:59,830
How disgusting.

686
00:34:59,830 --> 00:35:01,060
How am I disgusting?

687
00:35:24,660 --> 00:35:25,830
Qin.

688
00:35:26,230 --> 00:35:27,870
Why are you talking about me again?

689
00:35:27,870 --> 00:35:28,980
Everyone says shows are fake.

690
00:35:28,980 --> 00:35:30,730
- You two are real.
- Qin.

691
00:35:30,730 --> 00:35:32,530
Hurry and record
the behind-the-scenes footage.

692
00:35:32,620 --> 00:35:33,940
Her ears are red.

693
00:35:33,940 --> 00:35:34,940
No.

